{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"f9e022af89","title":"中央关于学习周恩来同志政府工作报告的通知（摘录）","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"62cdadf22e","index":0,"year":1965,"month":1,"day":14,"articleId":"f9e022af89"}],"tags":[{"id":"2d13338754","name":"指示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"523bb79e8f","name":"周恩来","type":"人物"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji47","name":"毛泽东全集第47卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/47-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji47":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"96f9fddfde","type":"title","text":"中央关于学习周恩来同志政府工作报告的通知（摘录）","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji47","articleId":"f9e022af89"},{"id":"c600319968","type":"paragraph","text":"外国一切好的经验，好的科学技术，我们都吸收过来，为我们所用。拒绝向外国学习是不对的，当然迷信外国，认为外国的东西都是好的，也是不对的，不论是迷信苏联，还是迷信西方，都不对，正确的态度应当是尊重科学，破除迷信。","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji47","articleId":"f9e022af89"},{"id":"6dbe8f1eab","type":"paragraph","text":"引进新技术不是一味攀仿，照抄照搬。学习外国必须用独创精神，结合起来，引进技术必须同自己钻研结合起来。对于进口的技术装备，必须加以研究，一般从仿制做起，进而结合我国的具体情况加以改进和提高","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji47","articleId":"f9e022af89"}],"page":{"id":"89f3eada17","publicationId":"maoquanji47","articleId":"f9e022af89","start":455,"end":455}}}},"__N_SSG":true}